<ul>
  <li>Once you have downloaded the Twitch client, run the installation and login to the Twitch client.</li>
</ul>

<p><em>Sign up to Twitch if you haven‚Äôt yet, or convert your old Curse account to a Twitch account.</em></p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_0.png" alt="Twitch Login" /></p>

<h2 id="installation-of-the-modpack-through-the-twitch-client">Installation of the Modpack through the Twitch Client</h2>

<h3 id="navigate-to-mods">Navigate to Mods</h3>

<p>On the top bar of the Launcher, look for the tab called Mods. Click on it and then select Minecraft.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_1.png" alt="Launcher Mods" /></p>

<h3 id="enable-minecraft">Enable Minecraft</h3>

<p>The Twitch client will prompt you to ‚ÄúEnable Minecraft‚Äù, which will restart the launcher.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_2.png" alt="Enable Minecraft" /></p>

<h3 id="install-minecraft">Install Minecraft</h3>

<p>Click on the Install button. Use the Advanced option if you want to select another location for the installation folder. The default folder is C:/Users/(your user)/Documents/Curse/Minecraft.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_3.png" alt="Install Minecraft" /></p>

<h3 id="browse-modpacks">Browse Modpacks</h3>

<p>After the installation is done, select Browse all Modpacks.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_4.png" alt="Browse Modpacks" /></p>

<h3 id="search-for-minecolonies-pack">Search for MineColonies Pack</h3>

<p>Type in the search bar ‚ÄúMineColonies.‚Äù Once you see ‚ÄúMineColonies Official‚Äù (<em>by Kostronor, H3lay, 1_Wissi_1. Asherslab81358, D3miurge</em>), click on ‚ÄúInstall‚Äù.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_5.png" alt="Selecting the Modpack" /></p>

<h3 id="launch-profile">Launch Profile</h3>

<p>Once the installation is finished downloading all the mods, click on PLAY.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_6.png" alt="Play the Modpack" /></p>

<h3 id="login">Login</h3>

<p>Login to your Minecraft account.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_7.png" alt="Login to Minecraft" /></p>

<h3 id="click-play-in-minecraft-launcher">Click Play in Minecraft Launcher</h3>

<p>Click the green play button if it‚Äôs already set to ‚ÄúMineColonies Official‚Äù. If not, then a couple substeps are needed.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_8.png" alt="Play Modpack" /></p>

<h4 id="open-profiles-list">Open Profiles List</h4>

<p>Click the green arrow (pointing up) to select your profile.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_8a.png" alt="Select Profile" /></p>

<h4 id="select-minecolonies">Select MineColonies</h4>

<p>Click the ‚ÄúMineColonies Official‚Äù profile. Then you‚Äôre ready to click Play!</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_8b.png" alt="Select Profile 2" /></p>

<h3 id="select-multiplayer">Select Multiplayer</h3>

<p>When Minecraft has loaded up, click on the Multiplayer button.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_9.png" alt="Loaded Minecraft" /></p>

<h3 id="select-our-server">Select our Server</h3>

<p>Finally, click on MineColonies Official 1.14.4! The server info will be set up already.</p>

<p><img src="../../assets/images/installation/twitch_10.png" alt="Join the Official Server" /></p>

<p>That‚Äôs it! Good luck, have fun. See you in the server.</p>
